 ensures even cooking of all the prawns.","At the end of <nobr>step 7<\/nobr> the sauce mixture should be quite thick and will be reduced by approx. one third; if not, cook for a further <nobr>5 minutes.<\/nobr>","Use the back of a spoon to spread sauce on each dinner plate to cover the inner two-thirds of the plate.","Instead of serving sauce with prawns, toss through hot pasta."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","35m","4 portions"]}